# Terraform state and lock files
.terraform/
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.backup
*.tfstate.*
*.auto.tfvars
!terraform.tfvars

# NOTE: .terraform.lock.hcl is intentionally NOT ignored — it must be versioned
# to ensure reproducible provider versions across environments and CI.

